OL,3,CThe reverend-turned-hairdresser
OL,4,Coffering free cuts to the most
OL,5,Cvulnerable
OL,7,FA community hair salon has opened in
OL,8,FPlymouth, offering free appointments
OL,9,Fto those facing economic or social
OL,10,Fhardship.
OL,12,FReverend Darren Middleton opened REV7
OL,13,Fin October and has welcomed 40
OL,14,Freferrals through its doors already.
OL,16,FThe salon, which is on Mutley Plain,
OL,17,Fhas referral days on Wednesdays.
OL,18,FDarren is helping some of the most
OL,19,Fvulnerable in the community.
