OL,3,CThe reverend-turned-hairdresser
OL,4,Coffering free cuts to the most
OL,5,Cvulnerable
OL,7,FHe is working with charities focused
OL,8,Fon addiction and rehabilitation,
OL,9,Fhomelessness, domestic violence, and
OL,10,Fmental health.
OL,12,FDarren said: "We make people feel at
OL,13,Fhome, we pamper them, give them great
OL,14,Ftreatments and haircuts. But we give
OL,15,Fthem that sense of self-esteem.
OL,17,F"The message here is 'you are loved'.
OL,18,FFor someone who feels the lack of
OL,19,Fthat, it's not just about the haircut,
OL,20,Fit's about the experience."
