OL,3,CThe reverend-turned-hairdresser
OL,4,Coffering free cuts to the most
OL,5,Cvulnerable
OL,7,FAfter suffering with drug and alcohol
OL,8,Faddiction for many years, Sharon
OL,9,FWilliams says REV7 has played a "big
OL,10,Fpart" in helping getting her life back
OL,11,Fon track.
OL,13,FSharon said: "I had more than 20 years
OL,14,Fof drugs and alcohol (addiction) and I
OL,15,Fwas agoraphobic for seven years. I
OL,16,Fwent down deep into a pit of darkness
OL,17,Fand it took a lot of years to come
OL,18,Fback from that, to heal myself.
