OL,3,CThe reverend-turned-hairdresser
OL,4,Coffering free cuts to the most
OL,5,Cvulnerable
OL,7,F"The first time I came here, I was
OL,8,Ffull of anxiety and nerves, but it was
OL,9,Fso welcoming. By the time I left, I
OL,10,Ffelt amazing because they had done a
OL,11,Fwonderful job with my hair which gave
OL,12,Fme confidence.
OL,14,F"I can't thank them enough, they were
OL,15,Fso understanding and so patient with
OL,16,Fme."
OL,18,FThe Methodist Church has put #250,000
OL,19,Ftowards the project, which will cover
OL,20,Fsome of the costs for five years.
