OL,5,Cvulnerable
OL,7,F"Through this salon, we aim to not
OL,8,Fonly provide great hair services in a
OL,9,Frelaxed, safe space but also help
OL,10,Ffoster a sense of dignity, self-worth
OL,11,Fand kindness throughout our community.
OL,13,F"We can be a listening ear and
OL,14,Fdemonstrate the power of caring about
OL,15,Fothers in a very tangible way."
